                        <outline text="Formal reduction of systems of linear functional equations #h ">
                            <outline text="Motivation #slide">
<outline text="Motivation: Similarities between linear differential, difference and $q$-difference equations and systems, e.g. Bronstein \&amp; Petkovsek (1996)"/>
<outline text="Want to extend progress made in differential case (Barkatou 1997, Pfluegel 1998, 2000)"/>
<outline text="This talk: extend local analysis from regular (Barkatou \&amp; Broughton \&amp; Pfluegel 2010) to irregular singular case"/>
                            </outline>
                            <outline text="Notations #slide ">
<outline text="$$\delta$$"/>
<outline text="$$\phi$$"/>
<outline text="$$\text{val}$$"/>
<outline text="$$\text{lc}$$"/>
