                            <outline text="We say that a generalised Shearing transformation $$(S^*,T^*)$$ is an __equilibrium Shearing transformation__ for the system $$\mathcal{D}= A\theta- B\delta$$ if it holds" listStyle="arabic">
<outline text="(i) $$\text{val}(S^*\mathcal{D}T^*)\le\text{val} ({S}\mathcal{D}T^*)$$ for all left-shearing matrices $$S$$, "/>
<outline text="(ii) $$\text{val}(S^*\mathcal{D}T^*)\ge\text{val}(S^*\mathcal{D}{T})$$ for all right-shearing matrices $$T$$. "/>
                            </outline>
