                            <outline text="Contributions/Novelty #slide ">
<outline text="Reduction of the pencil eigenspace problem to a matrix eigenspace problem, based on rank-factorisation of the matrix $$B$$. #novel:contribution" _note=" #proof&#xA;Referer: https://dynalist.io/d/F6qJJul5x4JWwZ4KTrIffFqu#z=zbwwaHCVkRlNB3_X5srVvUKc" colorLabel="1"/>
