<outline text="He creates __R___1, __R___2 and __R___3 and sends them to Alice, Bob and Charlie"/>
<outline text="Alice receives __R___1 = 01011000"/>
<outline text="Bob receives __R___2 = 10100110"/>
<outline text="Charlie receives __R___3 = 11010010"/>
<outline text="Later, Trent's server is compromised and he loses __M__. Show how he can reconstruct __M__."/>
