        <outline text="A __matrix pencil__ is an expression of the form $$A-\lambda B$$ where $$\lambda$$ is an indeterminate"/>
        <outline text="The matrix pencil $$A-\lambda B$$ is a __regular__ matrix pencil if the matrices $$A$$ and $$B$$ are square and the characteristic polynomial $$f(\lambda)=\det(A-\lambda B)$$ does not vanish identically: $$f(\lambda)  \not\equiv 0$$"/>
        <outline text="Otherwise, it is referred to as __singular__"/>
