            <outline text="Multiplicity "/>
            <outline text="Then $$\sigma(A-\lambda I) =: \sigma(A)$$ the set of eigenvalues of the matrix $$A$$."/>
            <outline text="We say that the spectrum is of __finite__, __infinite__ or __mixed__ type depending on whether the eigenvalues are finite, infinite, or both. "/>
