    <outline text="#definition A square matrix game $$G(A)$$ is called  __regular__ iff $$P(\lambda):=A-\lambda E$$ is a regular matrix pencil."/>
    <outline text="We denote $$c(\lambda)=\det(A-\lambda E)\not\equiv 0$$ the __characteristic polynomial__. "/>
