                    <outline text="Understanding Pareto Optimality: From Multi-Criteria Optimisation to Game Theory: A comparative exploration of efficiency and dominance across contexts #h ">
                        <outline text="Multi-Criteria Optimisation  The Basics #slide">
                            <outline text="Many real-world problems involve multiple conflicting objectives."/>
                            <outline text="Examples:">
<outline text="Design: Minimize weight, maximize strength"/>
<outline text="Finance: Maximize return, minimize risk"/>
