                            <outline text="Each component represents one players utility."/>
                            <outline text="Payoffs are evaluated jointly in $$\mathbb{R}^2$$."/>
                        </outline>
                        <outline text="Pareto Optimality in Bimatrix Games #slide">
                            <outline text="Definition: A strategy profile is Pareto optimal if no other profile improves one players payoff without reducing the others."/>
