                            <outline text="$$\begin{array}{c|c|c}&amp;    \ext{Cooperate (C)} &amp;    \ext{Defect (D)} \\\hline \ext{Cooperate (C)} &amp; (3,3) &amp; (0,5)\\\hline \ext{Defect (D)} &amp; (5,0) &amp; (1,1)\end{array}$$"/>
