<outline text="$$\tilde{A} = RA = \begin{pmatrix} \tilde{A}_1 &amp; \begin{array}{c} 0_{i-1} \\ e_i \\ 0_{n-i}   \end{array} &amp;\tilde{A}_2   \end{pmatrix}$$"/>
<outline text="$$A = \begin{pmatrix} A_{1\ldots j-1} &amp; A_j &amp;A_{j+1\ldots n}   \end{pmatrix}$$."/>
